# Sample htpasswd file
# Format: username:password
# Supported formats: plain, bcrypt
# Example entries:
# Plain text password (not recommended for production)
# plainadmin:plainadmin

# Bcrypt hashed password (recommended for production)
# admin:admin (bcrypt hash)
# admin:$2y$10$r8pL/rZQZnuxT81yJDiMFuJY..1ipJoKPShO8ud6TqJxmEDWY/yM.